{"tid":2428093,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港台電視部公共事務組總監王祿霞， 《頭條新聞》監製及 《香港故事》監製 遞信辭職","createTime":"2021-03-01T10:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-01T13:38:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ac7e1ad9fd915866eba0480ef103f4bc427de204","tid":2428093,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:00:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EvYqEWOU4AQL91B?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEvYqEWOU4AQL91B%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=a8452c86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n眾新聞獲悉，今日新廣播處長、政務官李百全履新，港台電視部公共事務組總監王祿霞同日遞信辭職，並有兩名監製辭職。消息稱，王祿霞辭職原因是被要求做許多超越其底線的工作，「頂唔到，辭職走」，故決定今日辭職；另外據了解是《頭條新聞》監製及《香港故事》監製辭職。<br />\n<br />\n三人亦都是公務員被要求宣誓後最先辭職的一批港台員工。<br />\n<br />\n早前《鏗鏘集》編導蔡玉玲因採訪查冊，被控兩項明知作出虛假陳述罪，王祿霞有份陪同她出庭。翻查以往港台顧問委員會會議紀錄，亦都見到會上討論到《頭條新聞》時，王祿霞在會上表示《頭條新聞》旨在監察政府和有影響力人士，不論政治立場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1366325796655165446/photo/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1366325796655165446%2Fphoto%2F1&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt15uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=4ee26ee6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1366325796655165446%2Fphoto%2F1&h=a9e5a98d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1366325796655165446/photo/1</a>"},{"pid":"5d503d9d58b49559313183f976eea3580eb05ae7","tid":2428093,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"respect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df51cf01dddb8528917f5b37df8ef8ea599577d1","tid":2428093,"uid":18477,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5eefd45e0c409f1f8848df5a8150c878773cac43","tid":242